  lines:
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CVale, ya estoy \xBFSe me ve bien?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CSe te ven\u2026 demasiadas cosas\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CConfirmo estoy viendo al menos tres figuras que no deber\xEDan mirarme
      as\xED\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CEs arte\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201DHolaaa :)\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201C:\u2026vale, t\xFA no vives en una casa, vives en un parque tem\xE1tico\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CEs mi sala de juegos :3\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CEso es\u2026 una m\xE1quina arcade?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CS\xED y tambi\xE9n tengo otra al fondo\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CY yo cosiendo a mano\u2026 perfecto\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201DYa estoy\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201D\xBFQu\xE9?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CNo voy a ser el primero\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DYo tampoco\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CNi yo\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201DYo s\xED\u2026 \xBFeso es un collar de perro?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201C\u2026No\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEst\xE1 literalmente colgado detr\xE1s de ti\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DHD, 1080p, sin duda\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CY bastante\u2026 est\xE9tico\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CEs- no es lo que pens\xE1is\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CNunca lo es\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CEs bonito\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CNo ayudas\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201COye\u2026 y esas bolsas\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201C\u2026No\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201C\u2026S\xED\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201C\xBFComida de perro?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CNO!\u201C"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CParecen pienso\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CProte\xEDna sabor \u201Cpollo y arroz balanceado\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CCon extra de\u2026 disciplina\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CES PROTE\xCDNA\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CPone \u201Chigh performance nutrition\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEso tambi\xE9n lo pone en el pienso premium\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: (...)
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CSois incre\xEDbles\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CBro, tienes collar y comida sospechosa en plano\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CLa narrativa se escribe sola\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CEsto es mejor que cualquier cosplay\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CAl menos yo no tengo figuras raras mir\xE1ndome\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CRespeta el arte oye\u201D "
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CDice el que tiene una figura en bikini en primer plano\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CYo tengo un traje tambi\xE9n\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEso me preocupa\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201DEsto ha escalado muy r\xE1pido\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201DVale, retiro lo del collar\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CGracias por eso eh\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CPor cierto, a ti\u2026 no se ve nada\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CS\xED, \xBFest\xE1s en una cueva?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEs mi habitaci\xF3n\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CNo se distingue nada\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CEnciende la luz :(\u201C"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CVoyyy\u201C"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: '"..."'
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201D\xBFEso es\u2026 ropa\u2026 o geograf\xEDa?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201CEso es una instalaci\xF3n art\xEDstica\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CHermano, limpia\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201CYo te mando dinero si quieres :(\u201C"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CNo es falta de dinero, es falta de\u2026 orden vital\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DTu habitaci\xF3n representa tu arco de desarrollo\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\"Oscuro Ca\xF3tico Sin terminar\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201DNecesita disciplina\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201DNecesita desaparecer\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DVale\u2026 recuento: yo tengo figuras, Ebo tiene telas oscuras,
      Pinky vive en un videojuego, Dario tiene\u2026 eso\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: EbonyDarkn3ss
    text: "\u201DY no te olvides del que  vive en la nada\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Pinky_Melody
    text: "\u201DA mi me gusta\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CConfirmado\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: Dario_OfDuty23
    text: "\u201CSomos un desastre\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: (...)
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "Ya es de noche...Obviamente s\xF3lo Makoto pensaba en quedarse despierto
      toda la noche"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: '"Oye"'
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DDime\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEstoy viendo el chat de comisiones que me ense\xF1aste antes\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CNo deber\xEDas estar ah\xED\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CDemasiado tarde\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CGenial\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CCliente: Pinky_MelodyUwU\u201D?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: " \u201CDime que no es quien creo que es\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CPuede ser coincidencia\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CNo es coincidencia\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CHay muchos Pinky\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CY muchos Pinky_Melody con dinero, fursona y obsesi\xF3n por lo adorable\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201C\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "Es Pinky_Melody\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201C \xC9ll no lo sabe\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CESO NO AYUDA\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CA m\xED si\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201DTe est\xE1 pidiendo un dibujo de su fursona?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CCy\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CY tu has aceptado?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CCy\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CIncre\xEDble\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CPaga bien\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CNo es el punto\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CEs bastante el punto\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CQue te ha pedido exactamente?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CAlgo bonito, suave, tierno, elegante\u2026 y rosa\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CEs literalmente Pinky describi\xE9ndose a s\xED mismo\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DTambi\xE9n quiere ojos con brilli brilli\""
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CVoy a fingir sorpresa\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201DTio, te das cuenta de lo raro que es esto?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CUn poco\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CTe est\xE1 pagando sin saber que eres tu????\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DEs como\u2026 anonimato profesional\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CY qu\xE9 pasa cuando se entere?\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201DOye igual no se entera\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: "\xA1"
    text: "\u201CSe va a enterar. Somos incapaces de guardar secretos\u201D\r\n"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201D\u2026\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CIgual se lo toma bien\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CExacto\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201DTe centras en lo importante, veo\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: MakotoUchiha69
    text: "\u201CPero funciona\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CDe momento\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  - speakerName: 
    text: "\u201CCreo que es momento de dormir\u201D"
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
  choices: []
